{"tid":1455491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[現場決定] 機場走唔走唔係最重要，我地應該睇下呢個moment連登仔點樣互屌話係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:00:57.000Z","uid":163842,"like":54,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7b9ae4e71c8788e81c263cddc2043e3c9e2eb7","tid":1455491,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"機場走唔走，我無意見，現場決定，因為佢地用身體去達成目標，用幾多，用唔用，佢地現場決定。<br />\n<br />\n重要既係，運動已經兩個月，次次黑警出動都會極大量post帶風向。少數既聲音就會極速被標籤為五毛同卧底。希望除左諗走唔走，都要正視呢個問題。唔好次次都內部分裂，令人不戰而勝得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n再講，你出得post姐嘆緊冷氣(今日我都係)，所以唔好咁撚肉緊話走／唔走就點點點。至於前線幾時都係重新諗一次，你呢個舉動對成個運動有咩幫助？如果有，值得既，就去做。<br />\n<br />\n例子：灣仔金紫荊同立法會"},{"pid":"6aef5477e79251179d67ae93596275116f3a34d9","tid":1455491,"uid":12468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"f3d5a427e2af4453161bc780bea33170dda4c488","tid":1455491,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"推，支持松場手足決定"},{"pid":"6c43f8cdbb8e8e99731e1c0e0e424390b40a9c3f","tid":1455491,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:06:14.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"fee098cec90db0bc83c69fe377082653845472eb","tid":1455491,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3d5a427e2af4453161bc780bea33170dda4c488","tid":1455491,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"推，支持松場手足決定"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea4435e34e3d952528db4d4c4215a9d8bd9ee03","tid":1455491,"uid":163842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"幫幫手推上熱門，想解決陣前自亂陣腳既問題"},{"pid":"cd07c53a3b0ad84236b0a83aac62cf76fce67f9d","tid":1455491,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n